    "So close — %lld cells left" : {
      "comment" : "Near-miss loss line on HEX boards (cells; square boards say tiles)",
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Niin lähellä — %lld kennoa jäljellä"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "おしい！残り%lldマス"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "So close — %lld tiles left" : {
      "comment" : "Loss consolation line for a last-cell near miss",
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Niin lähellä — %lld ruutua jäljellä"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "おしい！残り%lldマス"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sometimes no safe move exists — the board forces a guess, like one mine hiding in two identical tiles. When you survive one, Donpa stamps the odds your click had at that moment (50% here); your record keeps a luck line. The tracking is exact but conservative: a guess only counts when the game is sure no safe move existed — if it stays silent about a death, a safe move was still on the board." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Joskus turvallista siirtoa ei ole — kenttä pakottaa arvaamaan, kuten yksi miina kahdessa samanlaisessa ruudussa. Kun selviät sellaisesta, Donpa leimaa napautuksesi senhetkiset kertoimet (tässä 50 %); tilastoihisi kertyy tuuririvi. Seuranta on tarkkaa mutta varovaista: arvaus lasketaan vain, kun peli on varma ettei turvallista siirtoa ollut — jos se vaikenee kuolemasta, kentällä oli vielä turvallinen siirto."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "安全な手が存在しないこともある — 同じ条件の2マスに地雷が1つ、のように盤面が推測を強いる。生き延びると、Donpaはその瞬間のクリックの生存率を刻印する（この図では50%）。記録には運の行が付く。追跡は正確だが控えめ：安全な手が無かったと確信できた時だけ推測として数える — 死んでも何も言われなければ、盤面にはまだ安全な手があった。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sound" : {
      "comment" : "Settings: sound section title",
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
