        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "そのリンクまたはコードは有効なDonpaの共有ではありません。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "That was a forced guess (%@)." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "That was a forced guess (%@) — no safe move existed."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Se oli aito pakkoarvaus (%@) — turvallista siirtoa ei ollut."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "避けられない賭けだった（%@）— 安全な手はなかった。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "That's your own card" : {
      "comment" : "Alert title when a received share carries the player's own identity",
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tämä on oma korttisi"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "これは自分のカードです"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The classic trifecta with combined bests under 5:00." : {
      "comment" : "Achievement description (Decorations grid + future ASC)",
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Klassikkokolmikko alle viidessä minuutissa."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "三冠の合計ベストを5分未満にする。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Classics" : {
      "comment" : "Achievement title (see ROADMAP Progression spec)",
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Klassikot"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "クラシック三冠"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The connection dropped." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Yhteys katkesi."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "接続が切れました。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The corner toggle switches what a tap does: dig (open the tile) or plant a flag on a suspected mine. A long-press does the other one. Flags are your notes — they can be wrong, and you can clear them. Your first dig of a game is always safe." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Kulmakytkin vaihtaa napautuksen toimintoa: kaiva (avaa ruutu) tai liputa epäilty miina. Pitkä painallus tekee vastakkaisen toiminnon. Liput ovat muistiinpanojasi — ne voivat olla väärässä, ja voit poistaa ne. Pelin ensimmäinen kaivuu on aina turvallinen."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "隅のトグルでタップの動作を切り替える：掘る（マスを開く）か、怪しいマスに旗を立てるか。長押しでもう一方の操作ができる。旗はメモ — 間違っていてもよく、外すこともできる。最初の一掘りは必ず安全。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Drills family (leftmost in New game) generates boards that never force a guess — every board falls to pure deduction. Learn the patterns there, then speedrun them." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Soha-tyyppi (Uusi peli -valikon vasemmalla laidalla) luo kenttiä, jotka eivät koskaan pakota arvaamaan — jokainen kenttä ratkeaa puhtaalla päättelyllä. Opettele kuviot siellä ja ala sitten kellottaa."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "演習（新しいゲームの一番左）は推測を強いない盤面だけを生成する — すべて純粋な推理で解ける。ここでパターンを覚えて、タイムアタックへ。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The goal" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tavoite"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ゲームの目的"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The mine counter" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Miinalaskuri"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "地雷カウンター"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The save couldn't be read, so a fresh game starts on this board." : {
      "comment" : "Alert message under 'Couldn't load the saved game' — OK starts a new game on the same board",
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tallennus oli lukukelvoton, joten tällä kentällä alkaa uusi peli."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "セーブデータが読み込めなかったため、この盤面で新しいゲームを開始します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The signature didn't match. Ask them to share again." : {
      "comment" : "A short, honest reason for a rejected share when the signature didn't match.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Allekirjoitus ei täsmännyt. Pyydä uusi jako."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "署名が一致しませんでした。もう一度共有してもらってください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The top-bar counter is mines minus flags — how many mines you haven't marked yet. It trusts your flags, right or wrong." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Yläpalkin laskuri on miinat miinus liput — montako miinaa on vielä merkitsemättä. Se luottaa lippuihisi, oikeisiin ja vääriin."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "上部のカウンターは地雷数から旗の数を引いたもの — まだ印を付けていない地雷の数。正しくても間違っていても、旗を信じて数える。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Their card arrived." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Heidän korttinsa saapui."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "相手のカードが届いた。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "They got yours — now add theirs." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "He saivat sinun — lisää nyt heidän."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "相手には渡り済み — 相手のカードを追加しよう。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This clears your high scores and career stats on this device. Boards unlocked through play lock again." : {
